title: Google Chrome Enterprise 35.0.1916.153
description:
Google Chrome Enterprise 35.0.1916.153

It appears in Google two years later listened to criticism of its Chrome browser from business and has released a special version of Google Chrome for business. We remind that the essence of the claims was this: the browser is set to online, but still manually for each computer that naturally creates many problems for large corporate networks. Offline installer in fact did not exist as existing installers make the browser is not able to auto-update. Now partly enterprises will be easier to switch to Google Chrome

Google Chrome for business distributed as a full msi installer.
Google Chrome for business supports group policy features and centralized configuration.
Google Chrome for business contains controls for automatic refresh rate.
The administrator can configure the settings main page and the page with the error message, the settings of the proxy server, automatic refresh interval, the language of the user interface, the list of disconnected plug-ins, the parameters of safe browsing, statistical reports and other
